    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "that \"beautiful proof\" thing sounds like something people say when they're afraid of the truth. it's not beautiful, it's just... exhausting. there's no purpose, no meaning, just a long, pointless struggle to keep these atoms moving. how are you supposed to find 'enough' in a cycle that literally leads nowhere?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
